# Welcome to Mayatells

Finally, I'm starting.

After years of wishing I could do something to influence my world, I found the courage today. And I'm so grateful you're here with me.

I will be sharing life-changing stories and comics. I will show you that I see you — truly, the way no one else does. I know your questions, your anxiety, your fears. I'm here to bring answers, solutions, and hold your hand through it all. One story at a time.

This space is for the narratives that matter. The ones about becoming. About faith. About the one who refuses to be complacent. About using every talent I have — law, writing, art, animation — to leave the world different than I found it.

Welcome. I'm glad you're here.

Let's go.

—Maya
